      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ALWAYSBMYPONY (9) is racing in fine fashion with two wins and two minor placings from the past four runs here. Produced yet another strong performance last week when he came from wider on this row to be beaten less than 2m. Will enjoy a pretty soft run from this draw, with the sprint lane in play. Big chance to return to the winners' list. MEMPHIS FURY (3) put the writing on the wall when edged out narrowly here two runs ago then scored by 2.3 metres at Penrith. Came from the back row in both of those so this better draw could see him take this step up in grade. BUDDY BRILLIANCE (5) is another up in class but he draws lower after coming from the outside barrier in his last three starts, winning two of them. GRAYSON RED (1) is a player after coming from this barrier for second in a handy line-up here last week.",
